There&#39;s room for generalization, but here&#39;s one strategy for dynamically
creating TestCases..

As its written, you should be able to run it and see a green bar. If you&#39;re
interested in verifying that it really does verify the urls, add something
malformed or invalid to the list of URLs under test (urlsUT)

Best Regards,
Levi

